      and q.board_specialty = 'surgery'
      and q.scenario = 'ผู้ป่วยอายุ 40 ปี post-living-donor liver transplant 5 ปี for HCC + HBV cirrhosis — มา outpatient clinic for routine surveillance + planning for second pregnancy

Lab: stable graft function, HBV DNA undetectable on antiviral, immunosuppression on low-dose tacrolimus monotherapy

คำถาม: integrative survivorship + reproductive planning'
